Type: Screen Patrol Tablet
Price: 12.99

  • Screen Patrol's top layer takes scratch-resistance to a new level. With a 9H hardness rating, Screen Patrol cannot be scratched by knives or keys.
  • Touch-responsiveness guarantee hassle-free access and no delay

  • The oleophobic coating keeps fingerprints off your screen by repelling any and all oils. Cleaning your screen just got way easier.
